<br>
Epic was great in his day but that has past now. The new pets are superior, and even tho they have less hps then epic overall they offer much more to the 61+ mage then the old epic. I was farming a few days ago and found that the new air pet is just so much better. It doesn't have the epic damage output but then again it isn't that much lower in damage. Also the regeneration on the new pets makes them great farm tools. The new air pet mitigates damage much better then epic pet, and when you start using the new planes pets in the old world it becomes more visiable.<br>
<br>
Basically my suggestion is level to 65 and experience the best days that magicians have ever had. Zland Heart is very comparable in stats to epic while only costing 23kish. Much better then wasting months on a item that has marginal value, and is only going to get worse with the coming months.<br>
